title: NFL Week 6 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 6 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap the Cowboys' upset win in Seattle, the Packers comeback against the Dolphins and every other game from Week 6 in the NFL.
